posted 07-19-2001 09:36 AM &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
    &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/sb/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=edit_post&f=1&t=000659&reply_num=000003&u="><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/sb/forums/edit_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Edit/Delete Post"></A> &nbsp;&nbsp;<A HREF="http://forums.castersrealm.com/cgi-bin/sb/ultimatebb.cgi?ubb=reply&f=1&t=000659&replyto=000003"><IMG SRC="http://forums.castersrealm.com/sb/forums/quote_ubb6.gif" BORDER="0" ALT="Reply With Quote"></A>
